/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-atlas/execution/agents/library/factual/navier-stokes/vasseur-de-giorgi/beta-threshold-three-halves.md:5:source: "vasseur-pressure exploration-001; Vasseur 2007 Appendix"
