/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-atlas/execution/agents/library/factual/navier-stokes/vasseur-de-giorgi/choi-vasseur-2014-decomposition.md:5:source: "vasseur-pressure exploration-005"
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-atlas/execution/agents/library/factual/navier-stokes/vasseur-de-giorgi/choi-vasseur-2014-decomposition.md:10:Choi & Vasseur (2014, AIHP, arXiv:1105.1526) introduced a three-way pressure decomposition P = P_{1,k} + P_{2,k} + P_3 that simplifies the energy inequality by absorbing the k-independent piece P_3 into a time-dependent truncation level. This is a technical simplification of Vasseur (2007), NOT an improvement of the recurrence exponent beta.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-atlas/execution/agents/library/factual/navier-stokes/vasseur-de-giorgi/choi-vasseur-2014-decomposition.md:26:The mechanism: you "pay" for the pressure gradient by letting the truncation level rise, and since nabla P_3 is integrable in time, the total rise is bounded.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-atlas/execution/agents/library/factual/navier-stokes/vasseur-de-giorgi/choi-vasseur-2014-decomposition.md:30:In Vasseur (2007), the pressure was split four ways: P_k^1 (non-local), P_k^{21} (BOTTLENECK, non-divergence), P_k^{22}, P_k^{23} (divergence form, favorable). CV14 reorganizes:
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-atlas/execution/agents/library/factual/navier-stokes/vasseur-de-giorgi/choi-vasseur-2014-decomposition.md:43:The local pressure P_{2,k} contains the same non-divergence CZ-limited term that limits beta in Vasseur (2007). CV14 simply chose not to decompose P_{2,k} further because they don't need beta > 7/6. If one further decomposed P_{2,k}, one would recover the same P_k^{21}-type bottleneck. The P_3 absorption removes terms that were ALREADY favorable in Vasseur (2007) — it is a technical convenience, not a path around the bottleneck.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-atlas/execution/agents/library/factual/navier-stokes/vasseur-de-giorgi/pressure-galilean-invariance.md:5:source: vasseur-pressure exploration-003
