topic: Exact far-field pressure obstruction is a decomposition mismatch, not Vasseur's literal bottleneck
confidence: verified
date: 2026-03-31
source: "far-field-pressure-harmonic-loophole exploration-001; Vasseur 2007 Section 4 Proposition 3"
