+- **anatomy-of-averaged-ns-blowup-firewall exploration-002** — Pre-loading the closure stack mattered as much as pre-loading the positive mechanism reconstruction. Without the already-closed routes (generic pressure rewrites, LP cleanup, commutator reformulations, near-Beltrami perturbative hope), the exploration would have drifted back into dead leads instead of focusing on the remaining exact-NS firewall candidates.
 
